				<td colspan="2"><span>Many of those stories were under very EXTREME circumstances though.
<br />

<br />
Like a level 52 monk with elemental level gear, full 65 buffs, and about 20k in heal potions, soloing Vox/Naggy doesn't really make it a 1 group mob for normal people. 
<br />

<br />
There was a bug at one point where level 65 people found themselves suddenly at level 50.  So while they waited to get the levels fixed (no sense raiding elementals at level 50), many of them went to go kill Vox/Naggy for fun.
<br />

<br />
Get 6 level 50's with full elemental gear, level 65 buffs, and a few hundred AA's and they can do a pretty good job of 1-grouping the dragons.  <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-5.gif" border="0" alt="Wink" hspace="2" /></span></td>
