				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Lady Vox .. doable with 1 grp?<a name="36031"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 22 04 9:35 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Short answer : yes, Vox is 1 groupable
<br />

<br />
Long explanation :
<br />
Well last summer on Zeb a group of people tested Vox AND Naggy first with 3 then 2 and finally 1 group. We were successful all times =D Yes there was 65 buffs, the warrior and monk were heavily AA'd and things like clicky rune items and heal potions were distributed but not completely used. The one group was even done without a bard for resists, everyone just had gear to get them as high as possible with their buffs. It was not nearly as hard as you would think. The key was DPS. She went down fast all times.. choose your classes wisely and it can be done. (1 group was done with a monk, warrior, wizard, cleric, shaman and enchanter all 52)
<br />
Check the Zeb Crossroads board for old posts detailing it!</span></td>
